by `x ≤ y ↔ f x ≤ f y`. It is the unique relation on `α` making `f` a `rel_embedding` (assuming `f`
is injective). -/
@[simp]
def Order.Preimage {α β} (f : α → β) (s : β → β → Prop) (x y : α) : Prop :=
  s (f x) (f y)

